title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 380-1.1 - Applicability
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 380-1.1 - Applicability

State Regulations

The provisions in this Part shall be applicable to paid
family leave. The definitions included in Part 355 of this Title shall be
applicable to the sections herein. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12
§§
380-1.1

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
